lyrics:
[Verse]
Straight outta Bombay, with that Indian flow
My accent so unique, watch the rhythm go
Spittin' rhymes smooth, like curry and spice
Representin' my roots, makin' heads nod twice

[Chorus]
Indian accent, mixin' with the beats
Representin' my culture on these funky streets
From Mumbai to LA, we gonna do it our way
Rockin' the mic, 90s style, every single day
